Thank you @alan.walkerindia for giving me a chance to Witnessing @alanwalkermusic 🙌🏻 live in Jaipur feels like a dream come true—an experience words can barely capture.
The energy, the music, the lights—it all comes together in a surreal moment you never want to end.
Watching him perform in your own city, blending global beats with local vibes, is something truly unforgettable.
It’s more than just a concert; it’s a memory etched in time.
Grateful for the night, the music, and the magic. 🤍🪽

A night where reality met rhythm, and every beat told a story.
Still vibing, still reliving every second.

Happy Birthday to the Best Big Brother in the World!

Today, I just want to take a moment to tell you how much you truly mean to me. You’ve always been more than just a brother—you’ve been a protector, a guide, a partner in crime, and one of my best friends. From childhood memories filled with laughter and silly adventures, to the moments when life got tough and you were there with your support and strength—you’ve always shown up when it mattered most. 
I’m incredibly lucky to have you in my life. Thank you for being the big brother everyone wishes they had. I hope this birthday brings you everything your heart desires, and even more. I hope the year ahead is filled with amazing opportunities, new adventures, and moments that remind you just how loved you are. You deserve all the happiness in the world-and I’ll always be here cheering you on, just like you’ve done for me.
Happy birthday bhai. May this year be your best one yet. 🤍💜🪽
